<!channel> hi visual design team! now that we’re making small changes as needed and the UX team is working on creating the master document, we want to make sure everyone is following the same process. so if everyone could do two things moving forward as updates are needed that would be great - 
1. when a section is changing/being worked on, please pull the file you’re working on from the comp share folder and put it in the newly created PENDING folder.
2. When the change is completed please put the new file back in the comp share folder it originated from, with the same name so it simply replaces it versus creating a new file.
Let us or the UX team know if you have questions/concerns with the process and however else we can help keep things streamlined. Thanks!
Hey guys, you’ll also notice that we pushed the design meeting to 10am on Wednesday morning to review onboarding. Apologies that we couldn’t get it later in the day, it’s due to Scott’s schedule.
